info_dict.title: Toy Story (1995)
info_dict.actors: Tom Hanks, Tim Allen, Don Rickles, Jim Varney, Wallace Shawn

real_time_preference_list: I am looking for an animated adventure comedy movie that is suitable for the whole family. I would love to see some fantasy elements in the movie as well. I prefer movies with a runtime of about 1 to 2 hours. Additionally, I would be thrilled to see actors like Tom Hanks, Tim Allen, Don Rickles, Jim Varney, and Wallace Shawn in the movie.
